        "Description": [
            "**** Miners Amalgamated Loc. 163 ****\n******/ 'Stronger When United' /******\n\nRE: ARMED ESCORT\n\nWORK BRIEF:  \nA miner is in need of an escort while they scan [Complexity] around [Location] for possible new dig sites. You will be expected to protect them should any trouble arise. \n \nPAYMENT:\nStandard listed rate once the miner is escorted to their final destination. If hostilities do occur, a combat pay bonus will be issued.\nSPECIAL NOTES:\nThere is a good reason the miner is shelling out for an escort. The area has seen more than its fair share of trouble recently. Do what you have to so my miner comes back in one piece.\nAUTHORIZATION:\nBattaglia, Recco",
            "**** Miners Amalgamated Loc. 163 ****\n******/ 'Stronger When United' /******\n\nRE: ARMED ESCORT\n\nWORK BRIEF:  \nOne of our members needs an escort to watch their back at [Complexity] while they scan for potential dig sites around [Location]. If anyone attempts to interfere with them, it'll be up to you to protect them. \n \nPAYMENT:\nStandard listed rate once the miner is escorted to their final destination. If hostilities do occur, a combat pay bonus will be issued.\nSPECIAL NOTES:\nThere is a good reason the miner is shelling out for an escort. The area has seen more than its fair share of trouble recently. Do what you have to so my miner comes back in one piece.\nAUTHORIZATION:\nBattaglia, Recco"
        ],
